# Ruff Linter and Formatter

## Mandatory Post-Change Step

**After every edit to Python files**, run Ruff to lint and format:

```bash
ruff check . --fix && ruff format .
```

Or from project root:
```bash
python -m ruff check . --fix && python -m ruff format .
```

## When to Run

- After adding, modifying, or deleting Python code
- Before considering a task complete
- Fix any issues Ruff reports before finishing

## Commands

- `ruff check .` — Lint (add `--fix` to auto-fix where possible)
- `ruff format .` — Format code to project style
- `ruff check . --fix && ruff format .` — Lint with fixes, then format (use this)
